# PROJECTS

##SUDOKU

    [SUDOKU CODE](http://jrem090.github.io/SuDoKu/)
Code and built executable for SuDoKu game and solver. The application was written in C++ using Qt 5.5. To build open in Qt Creator and build the project.
##LOLCODE SCRIPTS

    [SUDOKU CODE](http://jrem090.github.io/LOLCODE/)
A collection of scripts written in the language LolCode. Currently only contains a rock paper scissors game
